    {
      "id": "PopularPost260791",
      "post_content": "Excellent protection card. It should always be used for its flash effect, as it not only saves the creature from a targetted spell or creature ability your opponent's about to use, but the look of annoyance on your opponent is fun to watch when the spell fails. For those who didn't go and read the errata, it grants protection from white without automatic destruction. Maybe someday if it's reprinted they'll clear that up.",
