    {
      "id": "PopularPost351774",
      "post_content": "Masques Block had some great mechanics to it, and playing creature enchantments at instant speed opened up tons of opportunities. It's been pointed out by other comments that this (like [Alexi's Cloak](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Alexi's Cloak)) can operate as a counterspell when played in response to your opponent's spell. Then it sticks around and offers all that goodness that comes with color protection. In Block play, a [Steadfast Guard](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Steadfast Guard) with a Cho-Manno's Blessing pro-blue was a win condition against Rising Waters. Playing Rebels with one of these in your hand is a very comforting feeling when your opponent is looking to torch your weak recruiters. ",
      "posted_by": "RaymondKHessel",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost351774\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_post\">Masques Block had some great mechanics to it, and playing creature enchantments at instant speed opened up tons of opportunities.  It's been pointed out by other comments that this (like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Alexi's Cloak\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Alexi's Cloak\">Alexi's Cloak</a>) can operate as a counterspell when played in response to your opponent's spell.  Then it sticks around and offers all that goodness that comes with color protection.  In Block play, a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Steadfast Guard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Steadfast Guard\">Steadfast Guard</a> with a Cho-Manno's Blessing pro-blue was a win condition against Rising Waters.  Playing Rebels with one of these in your hand is a very comforting feeling when your opponent is looking to torch your weak recruiters.  </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl06_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '351774'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy103744\">RaymondKHessel</span>\r\n                                (11/18/2013 9:57:02 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    